        <item>
            <title>【教学】泰国一键报警 App 注册，支援香港电话、一键即分享位置</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/05/thailand-tourist/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=thailand-tourist</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/05/thailand-tourist/life-tech/travel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 10:43:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅游]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Thailand Tourist Police]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[泰国]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1290047</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>泰国近日传出掳劫游客至「KK 园区」消息，令旅客人心惶惶。为保障游客，泰国警方推出了官方手机报警 App「Thailand Tourist Police」，游客能够利用这个 App 一键报警，并将位置分享予泰国警方。应用程式支援中文，同时可分享相片予泰国警方寻求协助。如果你最近会去泰国，就一定要预先下载这个 App 了。</p><h2>Step 1 下载 Thailand Tourist Police</h2><p>使用手机在 App Store / Google Play Store 下载「Thailand Tourist Police」APP。</p><p>下载连结：</p><p>Apple App Store：<a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/thailand-tourist-police">https://apps.apple.com/app/thailand-tourist-police</a></p><p>Google Play：<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=tourist.police.app">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=tourist.police.app</a></p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290058" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1348-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1348-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1348.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲下载 「Thailand Tourist Police」</p><h2>Step 2 注册帐户</h2><p>开启应用程式后，可见「Thailand Tourist Police」支援多国语言，你可以选择中文（简体）。选择中文后点击 Select。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290059" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_1.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择中文后点击 Select</p><p>现在你会看见注册画面，你可选择使用电邮注册，也可连结 Google / Apple 帐户。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290060" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1351-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1351-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1351-1.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可选择使用电邮注册，或者也可以使用 Google / Apple 帐户</p><p>小编选择使用 Apple 帐户建立 Thailand Tourist Police 帐户，那就无须输入电邮地址。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290061" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_2-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_2-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_2.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可直接连结你的 Apple 帐户</p><p>输入电话号码，接下来你可以点击下一步。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290062" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_3-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_3-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_3.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲输入电话号码</p><p>接下来你需要填写个人资料，填写好之后可以点击下一步。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290063" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1358-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1358-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1358.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲填好个人资料就可写「下一步」</p><p>阅读条款后滑动到最抵，点击「接受」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290069" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_4-535x580.jpg" alt="" width="535" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_4-535x580.jpg 535w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_4.jpg 830w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 535px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「接受」</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
